msgid ""
"Warning: WAIC estimate unreliable -- at least one effective parameter "
"estimate (p_waic) larger than 0.4. We recommend using LOO instead."
msgstr ""
"警告：WAIC 估計值不可靠——至少有一個有效參數估計值（p_waic）大於 0.4。建議改"
"用 LOO。"

msgid ""
"Warning: LOO estimate unreliable -- at least one observation with shape "
"parameter (k) of the generalized Pareto distribution higher than 0.5."
msgstr ""
"警告：LOO 估計值不可靠——至少有一個觀察值之廣義 Pareto 分配形狀參數（k）大於 "
"0.5。"

msgid ""
"WAIC and LOO cannot be calculated if no covariances are estimated for "
"independent variables with missing data."
msgstr "若未針對有缺失資料之自變項估計共變數，則無法計算 WAIC 與 LOO。"

msgid "Estimates might be biased -- %i divergent transitions after warmup."
msgstr "估計值可能存在偏誤——暖身後出現 %i 次發散轉換。"

msgid ""
"Bayesian Fraction of Missing Information (BFMI) was too low in %i chains -- "
"the posterior distribution was not explored efficiently."
msgstr "貝氏缺失資訊分數（BFMI）在 %i 條鏈中過低——後驗分配未被有效探索。"

msgid ""
"The Hamiltonian Monte Carlo procedure might be inefficient -- %i transition "
"exceeded the maximum tree depth."
msgstr "Hamiltonian Monte Carlo 程序可能效率不佳——%i 次轉換超過最大樹深度。"

msgid ""
"Low estimation accuracy for %1$s quantities -- the smallest Effective Sample "
"Size (ESS) is %2$.2f < %3$1.0f."
msgstr "%1$s 量數之估計精確度較低——最小有效樣本數（ESS）為 %2$.2f < %3$1.0f。"

msgid ""
"Inference possibly unreliable -- MCMC chains might not have converged; the "
"largest R-hat is %1$.3f > %2$.2f."
msgstr "推論可能不可靠——MCMC 鏈可能未收斂；最大 R-hat 值為 %1$.3f > %2$.2f。"

msgid "Dependent variables must be continuous."
msgstr "依變項必須為連續變項。"

msgid "Hayes number"
msgstr "Hayes樣版模型編號"

msgid "Model configuration number defined by Hayes (2022)."
msgstr "Hayes (2022)所定義的樣版模型編號。"

