msgstr "&#967;&sup2;"

msgid "Std. error"
msgstr "標準誤"

msgid "R-squared"
msgstr "R 平方"

msgid "Conceptual path plot"
msgstr "概念模型圖"

msgid "Statistical path plot"
msgstr "統計模型圖"

msgid "Model syntax"
msgstr "模型的 Lavaan 程式碼"

msgid "Model must be a directed acyclic graph -- it must not contain loops."
msgstr "模型必須為有向無環圖——不得包含迴圈。"

msgid "%1$s: Hayes configuration %2$s not implemented"
msgstr "%1$s：Hayes 設定 %2$s 未實作"

msgid "Estimation failed because of an internal error."
msgstr "估計失敗，因內部錯誤所致。"

msgid ""
"Full Information Maximum Likelihood estimation only available with 'ML' or "
"'Auto' estimators. Please choose a different estimator or option for missing "
"value handling."
msgstr ""
"完整資訊最大概似估計僅適用於「ML」或「Auto」估計法。請選擇其他估計法或缺失值"
"處理選項。"

msgid "<li>Some implied model variances are > 1,000,000</li>"
msgstr "<li>部分隱含之模型變異數大於 1,000,000</li>"

msgid ""
"<li>Some implied model variances are at least a factor 1000 times larger "
"than others</li>"
msgstr "<li>部分隱含之模型變異數至少比其他變異數大 1000 倍</li>"

msgid ""
"The information matrix could not be inverted. This may be a symptom that the "
"model is not identified. Possible reasons: <ul>%s</ul>"
msgstr "資訊矩陣無法求逆。此可能為模型未能識別之徵兆。可能原因：<ul>%s</ul>"

msgid ""
"At least one model is incomplete or no model is specified. Please add at "
"least one model and complete specified models."
msgstr "至少有一個模型未完整設定，或未指定任何模型。請至少新增一個模型並完成設定。"

msgid ""
"The AIC, BIC and additional information criteria are only available with ML-"
"type estimators."
msgstr "AIC、BIC 及其他資訊標準僅適用於 ML 類型之估計法。"

msgid ""
"<b>Important</b>: Parameter estimates can only be interpreted as causal "
"effects if all confounding effects are accounted for and if the causal "
"effect directions are correctly specified."
msgstr ""
"<b>重要</b>：只有在考量所有混淆效應並正確指定因果效應方向的情況下，參數估計值"
"才能被解釋為因果效應。"

msgid "Please check the model specification and lavaan syntax."
msgstr "請檢查模型設定與 lavaan 語法。"

msgid ""
"Linear test type cannot be applied to factor variables. Choose a different "
"test type or remove all factor variables from the model."
msgstr ""
"線性檢定型態無法應用於因子變項。請選擇其他檢定型態，或從模型中移除所有因子變"
"項。"

msgid ""
"The specified model does not imply any (conditional) independencies that can "
"be tested."
msgstr "指定之模型未隱含任何可檢定之（條件）獨立關係。"

msgid ""
"Partially standardized estimate because effect involves categorical "
"predictor."
msgstr "因效果涉及類別預測變項，故為偏標準化估計值。"

msgid "Moderation effect estimates are based on mean-centered variables."
msgstr "調節效果估計值係基於平均數中心化之變項計算。"

msgid ""
"Confidence intervals are %s bootstrapped. Standard errors, <em>z</em>-values "
"and <em>p</em>-values are based on the delta method."
msgstr ""
"信賴區間為 %s 拔靴法所得。標準誤、<em>z</em> 值及 <em>p</em> 值係基於 delta "
"法計算。"

msgid "Not all bootstrap samples were successful: CI based on %.0f samples."
msgstr "並非所有拔靴樣本均成功：信賴區間係基於 %.0f 個樣本計算。"

msgid ""
"Model does not contain moderated indirect effects for<br>which the moderated "
"medation index can be calculated."
msgstr "模型未包含可計算調節中介指標之調節間接效果。"

msgid "<em>p</em>-values adjusted for multiple comparisons with the %s method."
msgstr "<em>p</em> 值已採用 %s 法進行多重比較校正。"
